# ...but the per-family master alignments ARE runtime-critical: the ETL
# variants/isotype steps read data/<family>_tubulin/*.afasta. Without these
# in the image, collection fails for every non-alpha chain. (alpha's afasta
# predates the *fasta rule, which is why only it survived.)
!data/*_tubulin/*.afasta

